          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "TRN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " 1) Decreasing of foil activity was measured",
                "when an additional sample (1cm thick) of the same",
                "element was added in the neutron beam. Monitor foils",
                "were used to measure neutron yield fluctuation.",
                "So average total cross- section was determined - MISC1.",
                " 2) To measure total cross-section (DATA) , foils were",
                "irradiated together with silver foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " See METHOD, 2)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MISC-COL": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MISC1"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " < SIGcap*SIGtot > / <SIGcap>"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MISC2"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Correlation coefficient",
                "R=(< SIGcapture*SIGtotal>/(<SIGcapture>*<SIGtotal>))-1.",
                " For Cu-65 and Mn only R is presented in the article.",
                "En, keV                   R",
                "          Cu-65",
                " 450 +- 150             -0.46 +- 0.10",
                " 750 +- 150             -0.42 +- 0.15",
                "1100 +- 120             -0.33 +- 0.20",
                "1550 +- 120              0.00",
                "           Mn",
                " 450 +- 150              0.87 +- 0.10",
                " 750 +- 150              0.21 +- 0.07"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
